java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
public class EditorClient
extends javax.swing.JPanel

Description of EditorClient: This class is called EditorClient that is a client that launches the editor panel. It contains a String name that represents that clientName as well as a String host and an int that is the editorPort. We create a private socket that is for the EditorClient only and this will host its own port, host ID and host name. This also launches the main GUI for this portion of the edit.
